    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The DPAA Europe-Mediterranean Detachment continues to enhance operations through innovative strategies and improved efficiency. The U.S. delivers &#39;Devastating Combat Power&#39; to Iran this week, highlighting the ongoing military presence in the region. Colorado Army National Guard bids farewell to their commanding general after a distinguished career of 39 years. Zulu course graduates at Special Warfare Training Wing showcase exceptional training outcomes. Transcom&#39;s Air Refuelers are identified as its most critical assets, emphasizing their pivotal role in aerial refueling operations. The Army Aviation department has made significant progress with the delivery of the first autonomous-ready Black Hawk, marking a major leap forward in aviation technology. Departmental leadership extends an invitation to bring back troops separated due to vaccine refusal, highlighting ongoing efforts to address health concerns within the military. Innovation is highlighted through Airman-Built 3D Model strengthening air traffic controller training and Director&#39;s DCMA strengths acquisition transition visit. Small Business Spring Training focuses on fostering small business growth. JBSA fire safety officials emphasize safe evacuation over fire extinguisher use, reinforcing safety protocols. MICC leaders kick off the 2026 Golden Sneaker Strong Teams Challenge, encouraging strong team performance. The 34th Division Sustainment Brigade Change of Command signals a new chapter in brigade operations.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
